videos.headline: Houston's deep connection moves offense into Navy territory
videos.description: Houston QB D'Eriq King hooks up with Linell Bonner for the 32-yard completion.

videos.headline: Houston's QB scamper gives them early 7-0 lead
videos.description: Houston QB D'Eriq King takes the snap and sprints in for the nine-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Navy answers Houston with rush TD to tie game
videos.description: Navy RB Malcolm Perry gets the handoff and evades defenders on his way to the touchdown, tying the game at 7.

videos.headline: Houston fumble, gives Navy prime field position
videos.description: Houston return man John Leday fumbles the kickoff return and is recovered by Navy at the Houston 21-yard line.

videos.headline: Navy connects on rare deep ball, setting them up in Houston territory
videos.description: Navy QB Zach Abey hits Tyler Carmona for a 40-yard pass, moving them to the Houston 15-yard line.

videos.headline: Navy's FB gives them their second TD of game
videos.description: Navy FB Anthony Gargiulo takes the handoff up the middle for the 13-yard touchdown run, and gives Navy a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Houston knots score with rushing TD
videos.description: Houston QB D'Eriq King sprints left for the touchdown and tie the game at 14-14.

videos.headline: Niumatalolo: We have to clean up our offense
videos.description: Navy head coach Ken Niumatalolo breaks down his Zach Abey's play and what his team can do to pull ahead in the second half.

videos.headline: Houston gets game-sealing INT
videos.description: Navy QB Garret Lewis is intercpeted by Alexander Myres to cement the win by Houston.

videos.headline: Applewhite: Our defense stepped up in second half
videos.description: Houston head coach Major Applewhite explains how his team pulled out a win against Navy and how they feel about being bowl-eligible.

videos.headline: Houston hands Navy second straight loss
videos.description: D'Eriq King throws a touchdown pass and runs for two more scores in Houston's 24-14 win over Navy.
